text: DK3 may refer to: ==Media== * DK3 - the third and final studio album by American R&B;/pop group Danity Kane. * The Dark Knight III: The Master Race - a nine-issue DC Comics limited series co-written by Frank Miller and Brian Azzarello. ==Video games== * Donkey Kong 3 - the third video game in the original 'Donkey Kong' series by Nintendo. * Dungeon Keeper 3 - a cancelled PC strategy game by Bullfrog Productions. ==Transportation== * Droga krajowa nr 3, a national road in Poland
title: DK3 (disambiguation)
